column8: {'column_span': 1, 'is_header': False, 'row_span': 1, 'value': 'The Ranch Fire by itself, at 410,203 acres (100% contained) as of 19 September 2018, is the largest fire in California history.'}
{'column_span': 1, 'is_header': False, 'row_span': 1, 'value': 'Fatalities attributed to the fire include 1 firefighter and 1 civilian directly, 21 deaths in later mudslides.'}
{'column_span': 1, 'is_header': False, 'row_span': 1, 'value': 'This fire burned an additional 43,666 acres (17,671.0 ha) in Nevada, for a total of 315,577 acres (127,709.5 ha).'}
